high_descs: Pick up the soapbar and put it in the sink.
Turn the water on and rinse out the sponge in the sink.
Take the soapbar out of the sink.
Walk with the sponge to the toilet.
Put the soapbar next to the cleaning bottle on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Get the SoapBar from the top of the sink, clean it and put it on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the soapbar from the sink rim.
Put the soapbar into the sink, rinse it with water, then pick it back up.
Turn and go towards the toilet.
Place the soapbar on top of the toilet, next to the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Wash the SoapBar and place it on top of the Toilet.

high_descs: Turn around to face the sink.
Pick up the soapbar from the top of the sink.
Look down to face the sink.
Rinse the soapbar in the sink and take it out.
Walk to the toilet on the right.
Put the soapbar on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put the SoapBar on the Toilet.
